## Limitations

The analysis is based on available online resources and may not capture the full scope of XR applications in niche markets or emerging sectors. Additionally, the rapid pace of technological advancements means that the information may quickly become outdated. Further research and real-time data collection would be beneficial for a more comprehensive understanding of XR's impact on the business world.

